{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Monster Rancher'' episodes}}
This is a '''list of episodes''' for the [[anime]]'' [[Monster Rancher (anime)|Monster Rancher]]''.  The show is based on the ''[[Monster Rancher]]'' video game series made by [[Tecmo]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tms-e.com/english/search/index.php?pdt_no=190 |title=Title list page for the Monster Rancher anime series |publisher=[[TMS Entertainment]] |accessdate=2012-02-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091004014609/http://www.tms-e.com/english/search/index.php?pdt_no=190 |archivedate=2009-10-04 |df= }}</ref>  The episodes are directed by [[Hiroyuki Yano]], who also directed [[Daigunder]] and co-directed a [[List of Lupin III television specials|Lupin III television special]].  The Japanese animation studio [[TMS Entertainment]] produced the show.  The original run was from April 17, 1999 to September 30, 2000 on the [[Tokyo Broadcasting System]] in [[Japan]], and was later adapted to English.

